for bad people recently.

38
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,400
I did what I had to do
to investigate the case.

39
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,680
If I don't pretend to be
from a famous sect,

40
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,240
how could I get on the ship?

41
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,319
Investigate a case?

42
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:23,240
Aren't you after Vermilion Bird Wings?

43
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:29,680
You're an expert in the same industry.

44
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,240
Forget it.

45
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:38,560
You have great swordsmanship
and strong inner force.

46
00:02:39,479 --> 00:02:41,319
The martial world is dangerous.

47
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:45,080
How about we team up
to find the Four Divine Artifacts?

48
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,000
No thanks.

49
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:53,159
I never associate
with martial world frauds.

50
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:57,319
Martial world frauds?

51
00:02:59,080 --> 00:02:59,919
Forget it.

52
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,879
Gao.

53
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,360
The world is big.

54
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:04,319
We'll meet again in the martial world.

55
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:06,080
(Jingshui Boat)

56
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,080
Go.

57
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,280
(Yanyun City.)

58
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:22,000
(Gao Lingfeng
found a customs clearance certificate)

59
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:25,199
(to General's Residence in Yanyun City
in the courtesan's clothes.)

60
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,039
